HEADWORD: Flete
<hw>Flete</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Fleet</er>,
<pos>v. i.</pos>]</ety> <def>To float; to swim.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Whether I sink or <xex>flete</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fletiferous</ent>⟦br⟧
